{"tid":2389722,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"掌門30秒遭KO 死撐金句被註冊","createTime":"2021-02-01T05:50:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-01T06:08:49.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5f2a47d5dfc3eb141b66f58057a24250c583672c","tid":2389722,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T05:50:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210201/Q3THOT4M4JHRJLDXI3GXE4LXL4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210201%2FQ3THOT4M4JHRJLDXI3GXE4LXL4%2F&d=NiOc6rc%2FE9fikVhzT7%2F1G6jD3B6m7wr0JF9t5bmmazk%3D&h=59768492\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210201%2FQ3THOT4M4JHRJLDXI3GXE4LXL4%2F&h=0d0d2aff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210201/Q3THOT4M4JHRJLDXI3GXE4LXL4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n掌門30秒遭KO 死撐金句被註冊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/PkAMAKexcLkvChVBqP5MDvp2WGw=/3543x2362/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/IQVMQY2SN5EHRA3WMV5XDSQPEE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FPkAMAKexcLkvChVBqP5MDvp2WGw%3D%2F3543x2362%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FIQVMQY2SN5EHRA3WMV5XDSQPEE.jpg&h=42739211&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n內地打假狂人徐曉冬（左）曾約戰馬保國（右），但賽前十分鐘，警察突然入場，中斷比賽，徐被警察帶走。<br />\n<br />\n內地近年興起的武術打假風，讓不少所謂的「一代宗師」大出洋相。當中自稱「渾元形意太極拳掌門人」的馬保國，去年被業餘搏擊愛好者極速擊倒一事，至今仍為人津津樂道。馬事後的「死撐」的金句更成為熱話，官媒更刊文批馬譁眾取寵。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：內地整治格鬥界亂象  禁比武自封大師<br />\n官媒轟損傳統武術<br />\n<br />\n過去曾多次口出狂言的馬保國，曾經表示自己可「一隻手指可打低200斤（約100公斤）的肥佬」。去年5月，年約七旬的他與50歲的業餘搏擊愛好者王慶民相約對戰，但僅僅30秒，馬已被對方擊倒在地三次，最終被打至休克。馬事後堅稱，自己是「點到即止」才沒傷到對手，其後他一連串的「死撐」金句，包括「年輕人不講武德」、「耗子尾汁」（好自為之）等，以及對他自己武功的介紹是「三維立體混元勁」、「閃電五連鞭」等，更成為內地網絡的熱門用語，甚至被商家註冊為商標。<br />\n<br />\n身處事件風眼的馬保國去年11月一度宣佈：「遠離武林是非圈子。」其後又被揭。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n微博"},{"pid":"860d0747e7769ac26afe9c35a09b87f237a34a65","tid":2389722,"uid":20867,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T06:08:49.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">「年輕人不講武德」</code></pre><br />\n玩《王者》D上路畀對面越塔圍毆通常都打呢句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}